"title": "5893: insults",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5893",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Expressions of an individual's hostility or contempt for God and his servants or fellow human beings. Believers are to follow Jesus Christ's example in not returning insults.</p>\n<h2>Insults to God</h2>\n<h3>Insults to God coming from open unbelief</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:14-2Kgs19:16\">2KI 19:14–19:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:20-2Kgs19:23\">2KI 19:20–19:23</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:16-2Chr32:19\">2CH 32:16–32:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:14-Isa37:17\">ISA 37:14–37:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:21-Isa37:24\">ISA 37:21–37:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:29\">HEB 10:29</a></p>\n<h3>Insults to God coming through the suffering of believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:7-Ps69:9\">PSA 69:7–69:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:7-Jer20:8\">JER 20:7–20:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:3\">ROM 15:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:12-Heb13:13\">HEB 13:12–13:13</a></p>\n<h3>Insults to God lamented by the psalmist</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:18\">PSA 74:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:22-Ps74:23\">PSA 74:22–74:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:3\">PSA 10:3</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ insulted</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:31-Luke18:33\">LUK 18:31–18:33</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:17-Matt20:19\">MAT 20:17–20:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:32-Mark10:34\">MRK 10:32–10:34</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:67-Matt26:68\">MAT 26:67–26:68</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:65\">MRK 14:65</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:63-Luke22:65\">LUK 22:63–22:65</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:39-Matt27:44\">MAT 27:39–27:44</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:29-Mark15:32\">MRK 15:29–15:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:35-Luke23:39\">LUK 23:35–23:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:48-John8:49\">JHN 8:48–8:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:22-John18:23\">JHN 18:22–18:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:23\">1PE 2:23</a></p>\n<h2>Israel insulted</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:51\">JER 51:51</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:26\">1SA 17:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam21:20-2Sam21:21\">2SA 21:20–21:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr20:6-1Chr20:7\">1CH 20:6–20:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek21:28-Ezek21:32\">EZK 21:28–21:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:8-Zeph2:10\">ZEP 2:8–2:10</a></p>\n<h2>Kings, prophets and others insulted</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:27\">1SA 10:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:9-1Sam25:11\">1SA 25:9–25:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:14\">1SA 25:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam10:1-2Sam10:5\">2SA 10:1–10:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr19:1-1Chr19:5\">1CH 19:1–19:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:23-2Kgs2:24\">2KI 2:23–2:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:1-Neh4:5\">NEH 4:1–4:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl10:20\">ECC 10:20</a></p>\n<h2>The poor insulted</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:20-1Cor11:22\">1CO 11:20–11:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:1-Jas2:7\">JAS 2:1–2:7</a></p>\n<h2>Christians insulted</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:6\">ACT 18:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:14\">1PE 4:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:13\">ACT 2:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:32\">ACT 17:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:8-Acts19:9\">ACT 19:8–19:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:4\">1PE 4:4</a></p>\n<h2>The pain of insult</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:12-Ps55:14\">PSA 55:12–55:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:6-Ps22:8\">PSA 22:6–22:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:1-Job19:3\">JOB 19:1–19:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job20:2-Job20:3\">JOB 20:2–20:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps44:16\">PSA 44:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:3\">PSA 55:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:50-Ps89:51\">PSA 89:50–89:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps109:21-Ps109:25\">PSA 109:21–109:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:55-Lam3:63\">LAM 3:55–3:63</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:2\">1TH 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:9\">REV 2:9</a></p>\n<h2>Dealing with insults</h2>\n<h3>Avoiding insults</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov9:7\">PRO 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:10\">PRO 22:10</a></p>\n<h3>Not repaying insults</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:16\">PRO 12:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:39\">MAT 5:39</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:27-Luke6:29\">LUK 6:27–6:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:9\">1PE 3:9</a></p>\n<h3>Rejoicing in reproach for Jesus Christ's sake</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:11-Matt5:12\">MAT 5:11–5:12</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:22-Luke6:23\">LUK 6:22–6:23</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:41\">ACT 5:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:10\">2CO 12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:32-Heb10:34\">HEB 10:32–10:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:13-1Pet4:14\">1PE 4:13–4:14</a></p>\n<h3>Insult supposed but not intended</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:45\">LUK 11:45</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:1-Acts23:5\">ACT 23:1–23:5</a></p>",
